<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>The end of The Bachelor is fast approaching.</p>

<p>And it appears finalist Bella Varelis may have trouble keeping up with the fast-pacing dating show, as she made a rather awkward blunder on her social media account this week, </p>

<p>In a plug the show's upcoming home visits on Wednesday, the 25-year-old teased: 'And then there was four...,' along with a countdown.</p>

<p>Awkward! The Bachelor star Bella Varelis (pictured) may have trouble keeping up with the fast-pacing dating show, after a rather awkward blunder on her social media account</p>

<p>However, the date on her post was marked 11 months into the future, rather than 11 hours until the episode goes to air.</p>

<p>Bella swiftly deleted the post upon realising her mistake, and added instead 'can't wait for Locky to meet the most important people in my life.'</p>

<p>Sharing a photo of herself wearing a lace dress, the brunette went on to write: 'Who knew Survivor would be gearing Locky up to meet a protective Greek dad? p.s. dad is actually a big softie.'</p>

<p>Did you spot it? In what appeared to be plug the show's upcoming home visits on Wednesday, the 25-year-old teased: 'And then there was four...,' along with a countdown</p>

<p>Meanwhile, Locky will face his toughest challenge yet during Wednesday night's episode as he meets the families of his final four contenders .</p>

<p>And if the teaser trailer is anything to go by, Locky will be grilled by Bella's protective father as he issued a stern warning to the star.</p>

<p>'There's gonna be some hearts broken and the only heart that I care about is hers...' he warns.</p>

<p>Careful now! Locky Gilbert will face his toughest challenge yet during Wednesday night's episode as he meets the families of his final four contenders</p>

<p>To which, Locky replies: 'I totally understand that.' </p>

<p>The episode will also see the hunk questioned about his views on feminism.</p>

<p>'I'm on The Bachelor, some people might think I'm not the best guy to talk about feminism,' Locky is heard saying in a piece to camera.</p>

<p>The Bachelor continues Wednesday at 7.30pm on Channel 10 </p>

<p>Will she win? The remaining women competing for Locky's affections are Irena Srbinovska, Bella Varelis (pictured), Bec Cvilikas and Izzy Sharman-Firth</p>
